data.description: Come see this beautiful home positioned in a quiet cul-de-sac.  This house has been well maintained and is move in ready.   Features a large wrap around porch, 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths, beautiful LVP, large kitchen, finished flex space in the basement, fenced in back yard and beautiful trees and privacy.  The primary bedroom walks out to the porch, has a large walk in closet, private bath with garden tub, separate shower and dual sinks.  There are 3 additional bedrooms upstairs and a private office/reading nook.
